ll=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-sun size-4 scale-100 rotate-0 transition-all dark:scale-0 dark:-rotate-90\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"4\"></circle><path d=\"M12 2v2\"></path><path d=\"M12 20v2\"></path><path d=\"m4.93 4.93 1.41 1.41\"></path><path d=\"m17.66 17.66 1.41 1.41\"></path><path d=\"M2 12h2\"></path><path d=\"M20 12h2\"></path><path d=\"m6.34 17.66-1.41 1.41\"></path><path d=\"m19.07 4.93-1.41 1.41\"></path></svg><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-moon absolute size-4 scale-0 rotate-90 transition-all dark:scale-100 dark:rotate-0\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20.985 12.486a9 9 0 1 1-9.473-9.472c.405-.022.617.46.402.803a6 6 0 0 0 8.268 8.268c.344-.215.825-.004.803.401\"></path></svg></button></div></div></nav><div class=\"flex flex-1 flex-col\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-full max-w-7xl flex-1 px-4 py-6 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"flex gap-6\"><main class=\"min-w-0 flex-1\"><div class=\"mb-4 hidden justify-center lg:flex\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden rounded \" style=\"width:728px;height:90px;max-width:100%\" data-ad-slot=\"leaderboard\"></div></div><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"SoftwareApplication\",\"name\":\"Free Floor Plan Maker\",\"description\":\"Design floor plans and room layouts with drag-and-drop furniture placement and instant SVG, PNG, or PDF export.\",\"url\":\"https://freetoolshed.com/tools/floor-plan-maker\",\"applicationCategory\":\"UtilitiesApplication\",\"operatingSystem\":\"Web\",\"offers\":{\"@type\":\"Offer\",\"price\":\"0\",\"priceCurrency\":\"USD\"}}</script><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"FAQPage\",\"mainEntity\":[{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Is this floor plan maker really free?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Yes, completely free. No hidden fees, no premium tiers, and no sign-up required. The tool is ad-supported so it can remain free for everyone.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Do I need to create an account?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"No. You can start designing floor plans immediately without signing up or providing any personal information.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Is my data private and secure?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Your floor plan data never leaves your browser. All processing happens client-side on your device, so your designs stay completely private.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"What export formats are supported?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"You can export your floor plans as SVG (scalable vector), PNG (high-resolution image), or PDF (print-ready document). All exports are generated instantly in your browser.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"How many furniture pieces are available?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Over 100 furniture items are included across six categories: living room, bedroom, kitchen, bathroom, office, and outdoor. Each piece uses accurate real-world dimensions.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Can I set room dimensions in feet or meters?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Yes. Switch between feet and meters at any time. Dimensions are displayed on room edges and update automatically when you resize rooms.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Can I save my floor plans?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Yes. Your current design auto-saves as you work. You can also save multiple plans to your local history, duplicate them, or export all plans as JSON for backup.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Is there an undo/redo feature?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Yes. Full undo and redo support is included with keyboard shortcuts (Ctrl+Z and Ctrl+Shift+Z). Up to 50 history steps are stored.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"How does grid snapping work?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Grid snapping aligns rooms and furniture to a configurable grid (default 1 foot). This makes it easy to create precise, aligned layouts. You can toggle snapping on or off.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Is this a good alternative to SmartDraw or RoomSketcher?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Yes. Free Tool Shed's floor plan maker offers drag-and-drop room design, 100+ furniture pieces, grid snapping, and multi-format export — all free with no account required. SmartDraw costs $10/month and RoomSketcher requires sign-up.\"}}]}</script><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"BreadcrumbList\",\"itemListElement\":[{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":1,\"name\":\"Home\",\"item\":\"https://freetoolshed.com/\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":2,\"name\":\"Floor Plan Maker\"}]}</script><nav aria-label=\"Breadcrumb\" class=\"mb-4\"><ol class=\"flex items-center gap-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\"><li class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><a class=\"transition-colors hover:text-foreground\" href=\"/\">Home</a></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-right size-3.5 shrink-0\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m9 18 6-6-6-6\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-foreground\">Floor Plan Maker</span></li></ol></nav><h1 class=\"text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight\">Free Floor Plan Maker</h1><p class=\"mt-2 text-lg text-muted-foreground\">Design floor plans and room layouts with drag-and-drop furniture placement and instant export — a free alternative to SmartDraw, RoomSketcher, and Floorplanner. No sign-up required.</p><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"Person\",\"name\":\"James Nicolaus\",\"jobTitle\":\"Builder & Maintainer, Free Tool Shed\",\"description\":\"James Nicolaus builds and maintains every tool on Free Tool Shed. Each tool is designed, tested in real browsers across desktop and mobile, and shipped only after handling the messy edge cases — large files, slow connections, unusual inputs — that paid alternatives often hide behind sign-up walls.\",\"url\":\"https://freetoolshed.com/about\",\"worksFor\":{\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"name\":\"Free Tool Shed\",\"url\":\"https://freetoolshed.com\"}}</script><p class=\"mt-3 text-xs text-muted-foreground\">Built and maintained by<!-- --> <a class=\"font-medium text-foreground underline-offset-4 hover:underline\" rel=\"author\" href=\"/about\">James Nicolaus</a></p><div class=\"mt-6 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2\"><div class=\"rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\"><h2 class=\"text-sm font-semibold\">Drag &amp; Drop Room Design</h2><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Draw rooms, walls, doors, and windows with intuitive click-and-drag tools. Grid snapping keeps everything aligned and precise.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\"><h2 class=\"text-sm font-semibold\">100+ Furniture Pieces</h2><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Choose from over 100 furniture items across six categories — living room, bedroom, kitchen, bathroom, office, and outdoor — with accurate real-world dimensions.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\"><h2 class=\"text-sm font-semibold\">SVG, PNG &amp; PDF Export</h2><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Export your floor plan as a scalable SVG, high-resolution PNG, or print-ready PDF. All processing happens in your browser — your data stays private.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\"><h2 class=\"text-sm font-semibold\">Auto-Save &amp; JSON Backup</h2><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Your design auto-saves as you work. Save multiple plans to your local history, and export or import JSON backups at any time.</p></div></div><div class=\"mt-8\"><!--$!--><template data-dgst=\"BAILOUT_TO_CLIENT_SIDE_RENDERING\"></template><!--/$--></div><div class=\"my-8 flex justify-center\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden rounded \" style=\"width:728px;height:90px;max-width:100%\" data-ad-slot=\"mid-content\"></div></div><div class=\"mt-16 space-y-12\"><div data-orientation=\"horizontal\" role=\"separator\" aria-orientation=\"horizontal\" data-slot=\"separator\" class=\"shrink-0 bg-border data-horizontal:h-px data-horizontal:w-full data-vertical:w-px data-vertical:self-stretch\"></div><section><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-semibold\">Free Floor Plan Maker Online</h2><p class=\"mt-3 max-w-3xl text-muted-foreground\">Design professional floor plans and room layouts in minutes with Free Tool Shed&#x27;s Floor Plan Maker. Unlike SmartDraw ($10/month), RoomSketcher, and Floorplanner — which require paid subscriptions or accounts for full features — our tool gives you drag-and-drop room design, furniture placement, and instant SVG/PNG/PDF export at no cost. No sign-up, no account, no hidden fees. Your data stays in your browser and is never sent to a server.</p></section><section><h2 class=\"text-xl font-semibold\">Features</h2><ul class=\"mt-4 grid gap-x-8 gap-y-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground sm:grid-cols-2\"><li>Click-and-drag room drawing with live preview</li><li>11 room presets (bedroom, kitchen, bathroom, garage, and more)</li><li>58+ furniture items across 6 categories</li><li>Wall drawing tool with horizontal/vertical snapping</li><li>Text annotations for labels and notes</li><li>Grid overlay with configurable size (0.5, 1, 2, or 5 ft/m)</li><li>Snap-to-grid for precise placement</li><li>Resize handles with 8-point selection</li><li>Rotation with 15-degree snapping</li><li>Dimension labels on rooms (feet or meters)</li><li>Bring to front / send to back layer ordering</li><li>Lock elements to prevent accidental edits</li><li>50-step undo/redo history</li><li>Copy and paste elements with new IDs</li><li>SVG, PNG (1x/2x/4x), and PDF export</li><li>PDF export with A4 or Letter paper size</li><li>Auto-save draft to local storage</li><li>Save multiple plans to local history</li><li>JSON export/import for backup and sharing</li><li>Keyboard shortcuts for all common actions</li><li>Zoom and pan with scroll wheel and controls</li><li>Feet and meters unit support</li><li>Client-side only — data never leaves your browser</li></ul></section><section><h2 class=\"text-xl font-semibold\">How to Create a Floor Plan</h2><ol class=\"mt-4 space-y-4\"><li><p class=\"font-medium\">1. Set up your plan dimensions</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Choose the width, height, and measurement unit (feet or meters) for your floor plan in the right panel. Enable grid snapping for precise alignment.</p></li><li><p class=\"font-medium\">2. Draw rooms</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Select the Room tool (R) and click-drag on the canvas to draw rectangular rooms. Choose from 11 room presets — bedroom, kitchen, bathroom, living room, and more — each with a default size and color.</p></li><li><p class=\"font-medium\">3. Add walls and text</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Use the Wall tool (W) to draw walls between rooms. Walls automatically snap to horizontal or vertical alignment. Add text labels with the Text tool (T) for annotations.</p></li><li><p class=\"font-medium\">4. Place furniture</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Open the Furniture palette (F) and browse 58+ items across six categories: living room, bedroom, kitchen, bathroom, office, and outdoor. Click any item to place it on the canvas, then drag to position.</p></li><li><p class=\"font-medium\">5. Export your floor plan</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Click Export in the top bar and choose SVG for scalable graphics, PNG for high-resolution images (up to 4x), or PDF for print-ready documents on A4 or Letter paper.</p></li></ol></section><section><h2 class=\"text-xl font-semibold\">Free Tool Shed vs Paid Floor Plan Software</h2><div class=\"mt-4 overflow-x-auto\"><table class=\"w-full min-w-[600px] border-collapse text-sm\"><thead><tr class=\"border-b border-border text-left\"><th class=\"py-2 pr-4 font-semibold\">Feature</th><th class=\"py-2 pr-4 font-semibold\">Free Tool Shed</th><th class=\"py-2 pr-4 font-semibold\">SmartDraw</th><th class=\"py-2 pr-4 font-semibold\">RoomSketcher</th><th class=\"py-2 font-semibold\">Floorplanner</th></tr></thead><tbody class=\"text-muted-foreground\"><tr class=\"border-b border-border/50\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">Price</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 font-medium text-foreground\">Free forever</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">$9.95/mo</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">$49/year</td><td class=\"py-2  \">Free (limited) / $4.99+</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-border/50\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">Account Required</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 font-medium text-foreground\">No</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">Yes</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">Yes</td><td class=\"py-2  \">Yes</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-border/50\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">SVG Export</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 font-medium text-foreground\">Free</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">Paid</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">No</td><td class=\"py-2  \">No</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-border/50\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">PNG Export</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 font-medium text-foreground\">Free (up to 4x)</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">Paid</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">Paid</td><td class=\"py-2  \">Paid</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-border/50\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">PDF Export</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 font-medium text-foreground\">Free</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">Paid</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">Paid</td><td class=\"py-2  \">Paid</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-border/50\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">Furniture Library</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 font-medium text-foreground\">95+ items</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">500+</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">1000+</td><td class=\"py-2  \">150+</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-border/50\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">Doors &amp; Windows</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 font-medium text-foreground\">12 items</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">Yes</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">Yes</td><td class=\"py-2  \">Yes</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-border/50\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">Electrical Symbols</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 font-medium text-foreground\">14 items</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">Yes</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">Limited</td><td class=\"py-2  \">No</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-border/50\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">Starter Templates</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 font-medium text-foreground\">5 layouts</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">100+</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">20+</td><td class=\"py-2  \">10+</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-border/50\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">Blueprint Underlay</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 font-medium text-foreground\">Free</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">Yes</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">Paid</td><td class=\"py-2  \">Paid</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-border/50\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">Smart Alignment</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 font-medium text-foreground\">Yes</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">Yes</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">Yes</td><td class=\"py-2  \">Yes</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-border/50\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">Room Area Display</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 font-medium text-foreground\">Auto-calculated</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">Yes</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">Yes</td><td class=\"py-2  \">Yes</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-border/50\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">Room Drawing</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 font-medium text-foreground\">Click-drag</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">Click-drag</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">Click-drag</td><td class=\"py-2  \">Click-drag</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-border/50\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">Data Privacy</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 font-medium text-foreground\">Client-side only</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">Cloud-stored</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">Cloud-stored</td><td class=\"py-2  \">Cloud-stored</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-border/50\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">Undo/Redo</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 font-medium text-foreground\">50 steps</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">Unlimited</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">Limited</td><td class=\"py-2  \">Limited</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-border/50\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">JSON Backup</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 font-medium text-foreground\">Yes</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">No</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">No</td><td class=\"py-2  \">No</td></tr></tbody></table></div></section><section><h2 class=\"text-xl font-semibold\">Frequently Asked Questions</h2><div class=\"mt-4 space-y-3\"><details class=\"group rounded-lg border border-border px-4 py-3\"><summary class=\"cursor-pointer font-medium\">Is this floor plan maker really free?</summary><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Yes, completely free. No hidden fees, no premium tiers, and no sign-up required. The tool is ad-supported so it can remain free for everyone.</p></details><details class=\"group rounded-lg border border-border px-4 py-3\"><summary class=\"cursor-pointer font-medium\">Do I need to create an account?</summary><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">No. You can start designing your floor plan immediately without signing up or providing any personal information.</p></details><details class=\"group rounded-lg border border-border px-4 py-3\"><summary class=\"cursor-pointer font-medium\">Can I export my floor plan as a PDF?</summary><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Yes — click Export in the top bar and select PDF. Choose between A4 and Letter paper sizes. The PDF includes a header with your plan name and dimensions, and the layout automatically switches between portrait and landscape orientation.</p></details><details class=\"group rounded-lg border border-border px-4 py-3\"><summary class=\"cursor-pointer font-medium\">What export formats are available?</summary><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Three formats: SVG for scalable vector graphics (perfect for further editing), PNG at 1x, 2x, or 4x resolution for high-quality images, and PDF for print-ready documents.</p></details><details class=\"group rounded-lg border border-border px-4 py-3\"><summary class=\"cursor-pointer font-medium\">Is my data private and secure?</summary><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Your floor plan data never leaves your browser. All processing happens client-side on your device, so your designs and measurements stay completely private.</p></details><details class=\"group rounded-lg border border-border px-4 py-3\"><summary class=\"cursor-pointer font-medium\">Can I save multiple floor plans?</summary><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Yes. Save plans to your local history, name them, and switch between versions. You can also export all plans as JSON for backup and import them later on any computer.</p></details><details class=\"group rounded-lg border border-border px-4 py-3\"><summary class=\"cursor-pointer font-medium\">What furniture is available?</summary><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Over 58 furniture items across six categories: living room (sofas, tables, TV units), bedroom (beds, dressers, nightstands), kitchen (stoves, sinks, islands), bathroom (tubs, toilets, vanities), office (desks, chairs, bookshelves), and outdoor (benches, grills, planters).</p></details><details class=\"group rounded-lg border border-border px-4 py-3\"><summary class=\"cursor-pointer font-medium\">Can I change the measurement units?</summary><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Yes. Switch between feet and meters at any time in the Plan Settings panel on the right side. All dimensions, grid sizes, and measurements update automatically.</p></details><details class=\"group rounded-lg border border-border px-4 py-3\"><summary class=\"cursor-pointer font-medium\">What keyboard shortcuts are available?</summary><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">V for select tool, R for room drawing, W for wall drawing, T for text, F to toggle furniture palette, Delete to remove selected elements, Ctrl+Z to undo, Ctrl+Shift+Z to redo, Ctrl+C to copy, and Ctrl+V to paste.</p></details><details class=\"group rounded-lg border border-border px-4 py-3\"><summary class=\"cursor-pointer font-medium\">How accurate are the measurements?</summary><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">The tool uses a precise coordinate system with configurable grid sizes (0.5, 1, 2, or 5 units). Snap-to-grid ensures elements align precisely. Dimension labels display in feet-inches or meters depending on your unit setting.</p></details></div></section></div><!--$--><!--/$--></main><aside class=\"hidden w-[300px] shrink-0 lg:block\"><div class=\"sticky top-20\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden rounded \" style=\"width:300px;height:250px;max-width:100%\" data-ad-slot=\"sidebar\"></div><div id=\"tool-guide-portal\"></div></div></aside></div></div></div><footer class=\"border-t border-border bg-muted/40\"><div class=\"mx-auto flex max-w-7xl flex-col items-center gap-4 px-4 py-8 sm:flex-row sm:justify-between sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><p class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground\">© <!-- -->2026<!-- --> Free Tool Shed. All rights reserved.</p><nav class=\"flex gap-4 text-sm text-muted-foreground\"><a class=\"transition-colors hover:text-foreground\" href=\"/about\">About</a><a class=\"transition-colors hover: